<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero__content">
                <h1>For Candidates</h1>
                <p>Discover exciting opportunities with top tech startups and take your career to the next level.</p>
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <a href="/candidates/register" class="btn btn-secondary mr-2">Register Now</a>
                    <a href="/candidates/jobs" class="btn btn-outline">Browse Jobs</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section__header">
                <h2>Why Choose TalentQuery?</h2>
                <p>We're dedicated to connecting talented professionals with the right opportunities in the tech industry.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="feature">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">Top Tech Opportunities</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">Access exclusive job openings with innovative tech startups and established companies.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="feature">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">Personalized Matching</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">We match your skills and career goals with the perfect opportunities.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="feature">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">Career Growth</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">Get guidance and support to advance your career in the tech industry.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works Section -->
    <section class="section section--alt">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section__header">
                <h2>How It Works</h2>
                <p>Our simple process helps you find your dream job in the tech industry.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col col-md-3 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="feature text-center">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">1. Create Profile</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">Register and create your professional profile with your skills and experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-3 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="feature text-center">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-file-upload"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">2. Upload CV</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">Upload your CV and showcase your qualifications to potential employers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-3 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="feature text-center">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">3. Browse Jobs</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">Explore job opportunities that match your skills and career goals.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-3 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="feature text-center">
                        <div class="feature__icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="feature__title">4. Apply</h4>
                        <p class="feature__text">Apply to positions with just a few clicks and track your applications.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/candidates/register" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tech Roles Section -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section__header">
                <h2>Tech Roles We Specialize In</h2>
                <p>We connect talented professionals with opportunities across various tech domains.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__content">
                            <h3 class="card__title">Development</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Front-end Developers</li>
                                <li>Back-end Developers</li>
                                <li>Full-stack Developers</li>
                                <li>Mobile Developers</li>
                                <li>Game Developers</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__content">
                            <h3 class="card__title">Data & AI</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Data Scientists</li>
                                <li>Data Engineers</li>
                                <li>Machine Learning Engineers</li>
                                <li>AI Specialists</li>
                                <li>Business Intelligence Analysts</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__content">
                            <h3 class="card__title">Infrastructure</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>DevOps Engineers</li>
                                <li>Cloud Architects</li>
                                <li>System Administrators</li>
                                <li>Network Engineers</li>
                                <li>Security Specialists</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__content">
                            <h3 class="card__title">Design</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>UX/UI Designers</li>
                                <li>Product Designers</li>
                                <li>Graphic Designers</li>
                                <li>Interaction Designers</li>
                                <li>Visual Designers</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__content">
                            <h3 class="card__title">Management</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Product Managers</li>
                                <li>Project Managers</li>
                                <li>Technical Team Leads</li>
                                <li>Scrum Masters</li>
                                <li>Agile Coaches</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__content">
                            <h3 class="card__title">Quality Assurance</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>QA Engineers</li>
                                <li>Test Automation Engineers</li>
                                <li>Performance Testers</li>
                                <li>Security Testers</li>
                                <li>QA Analysts</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section class="section section--alt">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section__header">
                <h2>Success Stories</h2>
                <p>Hear from candidates who found their dream jobs through TalentQuery.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <p class="testimonial__text">"TalentQuery helped me find a position that perfectly matched my skills and career goals. The process was smooth and professional from start to finish."</p>
                        <p class="testimonial__author">Maria Rodriguez</p>
                        <p class="testimonial__position">Senior Frontend Developer</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <p class="testimonial__text">"I was looking for a new challenge in the AI field, and TalentQuery connected me with an innovative startup that was the perfect fit for my expertise."</p>
                        <p class="testimonial__author">David Chen</p>
                        <p class="testimonial__position">Machine Learning Engineer</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-md-4 col-sm-12">
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <p class="testimonial__text">"The personalized approach and industry knowledge of the TalentQuery team made all the difference in my job search. They truly understand the tech market."</p>
                        <p class="testimonial__author">Sarah Johnson</p>
                        <p class="testimonial__position">DevOps Specialist</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section__header">
                <h2>Ready to Take the Next Step in Your Tech Career?</h2>
                <p>Join TalentQuery today and discover exciting opportunities with innovative tech companies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <a href="/candidates/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Register Now</a>
                <a href="/candidates/jobs" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg ml-3">Browse Jobs</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
